{"bangumi":{"date":"2017-11-03","platform":"OVA","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/56/39/194852_KJ2a6.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/56/39/194852_KJ2a6.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/56/39/194852_KJ2a6.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/56/39/194852_KJ2a6.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/56/39/194852_KJ2a6.jpg"},"summary":"在被皑皑白雪所覆盖的终末世界，从被人称为“终点”的地方来到这里的不可思议的两位少女。\r\n一位名叫柯蓉(Chron)，有着宛如在盛夏日灿放的向日葵般的明朗笑容，对什么都兴趣盎然。\r\n另一位名为艾思卡(Escha)，像是拂晓时分的皎月般的柔和神秘的眼眸让人印象深刻。\r\n虽然给人带来的印象完全不同，但是有某处相似着的两人。\r\n两人称呼这个现代社会为“中转处”。\r\n两人在“中转处”接触到的音乐与景色、与各种人的相逢与交流，给这个世界似乎带来了一点一点的变化……。","name":"エスカクロン","name_cn":"ESCHA CHRON","tags":[{"name":"OVA","count":95,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2017","count":54,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Lerche","count":50,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":48,"total_cont":0},{"name":"水島精二","count":38,"total_cont":0},{"name":"百合","count":17,"total_cont":0},{"name":"水岛精二","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"安済知佳","count":12,"total_cont":0},{"name":"髙橋龍也","count":11,"total_cont":0},{"name":"安野希世乃","count":11,"total_cont":0},{"name":"山口光","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"治愈","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"山口ひかる","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"水無月徹","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"ESCHA","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"高桥龙也","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"独立ova","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2017年11月","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"已下载","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"undefined","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"オリジナル","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"科幻","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"还行","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"35","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"新5分","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"补番","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"『OVA』","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"单元剧","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"6+","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"ESCHA CHRON"},{"key":"